tip.text: Excellent view, nice strong cappuccino, perfect lounge music. Good for quick bite as well.
Big portions,though nothing special overall.Quick service,family friendly,good quality ingredients but somehow not savory enough.Pricey but ok for Mykonos standards
Friendly, efficient service! Impressive burgers, tasty pasta with the fresh salmon or the brazed free range rooster from Naxos island. Amazing "γκογκλες". Take the nice n easy salad.
Try all the mezze, if possible, but especially the cuttlefish pilaf, the mussels, the little stuffed vine-leaves, and the red cabbage salad.Exceptional service
Great for brunch!Try the croquet monsieur and the scrabbled eggs with smoked salmon on avocado toast. Mouthwatering. Slow service though.
Amazing biscuit banana dessert, chocolate "mosaiko" and kanafeh with kaimaki ice cream to die for!

tip.text: Best beach in Greece!!!

Warm friendly service.Relaxing seating by the sea.Try oven baked sardines,marinated anchovies, smoked eggplant,fishroe spread, local sausage,sea urchin. Take the local beer Nisos instead of house wine
We took the fairfax sandwich and the slut plate. Both delicious.

tip.text: The salmon egg plate was tasty but nothing special overall. Good strong Italian cappuccino though. Slow yet friendly service. Pretty crowded
Nice ambience.Welcoming champagne on the house and farewell cookies.Nice Mane Lobster linguini, guacamole + Caesar's salad
Great meat selection but slow service. Get the yucca fries
Creme de la creme French toast and mounds of pleasure pancake and the hash it up eggs!!! Absolutely perfect!!
Πρωτότυπη διακόσμηση, περιορισμένο μενού αλλά ενδιαφέρουσες γεύσεις. Πολυ φιλικό service και ταιριαστές με τον χώρο οι μουσικές επιλογές!
Loved the quinoa salad, the spinach/zucchini pie and the rice cake! The owner couldn't be any friendlier!
Great location, helpful staff, good value for money. Needs slight renovation otherwise smart choice in Shanghai.
